  "detailed_description": "Show off your skills & reflexes in this frantic <strong>gallery shooter</strong> action arcade, filled with bullets, bots and explosions. You play as <strong>Erin Saver</strong>, carrying out her personal vendetta against the criminal <strong>Wildbots</strong>.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Super intense arcade shooting action.<br></li><li>One unique challenging boss per stage!<br></li><li>Unlockable \"Extra Missions\" mode.<br></li><li>Three difficulty modes: Hard, Normal and Easy.<br></li><li>Polished and colorful pixel art visuals.<br></li><li>Catchy 90's synth-rock soundtrack.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Show off your skills & reflexes in this frantic <strong>gallery shooter</strong> action arcade, filled with bullets, bots and explosions. You play as <strong>Erin Saver</strong>, carrying out her personal vendetta against the criminal <strong>Wildbots</strong>.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Super intense arcade shooting action.<br></li><li>One unique challenging boss per stage!<br></li><li>Unlockable \"Extra Missions\" mode.<br></li><li>Three difficulty modes: Hard, Normal and Easy.<br></li><li>Polished and colorful pixel art visuals.<br></li><li>Catchy 90's synth-rock soundtrack.</li></ul>",
